    "# Winter Olympics (2002-2022) Data Anlysis "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "068f7ae1-286f-473c-b75b-fb13e5fb4b58",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "I focused on post-2000 Winter Olympic data to ensure consistency in event structure and participation levels. Since the number of events has grown significantly over time, using modern data allows for more accurate comparisons across countries without historical bias. For example, sports, such as alpinism and military ski patrol, are no longer part of the games since 1948."
   ]
  },
