  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "c90f0905-6c67-47e8-bee5-807b932f7833",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Winter Olympics popularity may be contributed from certain sport popularity. The graph below displays the top sports (most games) and their growth over time. Cross country skiing has always been the top sport, but speed skating grew especially in 2018, which ties as the top sport with cross country skiing.  "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
