  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "223c0d4e-8afb-4d3c-8895-ed904735b347",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Step 4: Feature Relationships \n",
    "* Top Sports by Top Countries breakdown\n",
    "* Sport popularity vs gold share correlation"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d1d1c077-6d8a-4d18-b5b4-cfffd652230e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Which sports did top countries dominate?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "470220f7-73d8-4482-8ce6-bbcafa16b5f4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "The bar graph below breaks down the top 3 sports each of the top countries dominated in (won the most medal). This distribution demonstrated whether a country dominated one certain sport or are all rounderers. For example, Norway shows that they are dominate in specific sports, Cross Country Skiing, instead of winning evenly across different sports."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 26,
   "id": "9f774555-1929-44b8-8af6-3ab26a4543e2",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Created df for only top 6 countries with the most winnings\n",
    "\n",
    "top_countries = medal_counts.head(6).index\n",
    "top_df = df.loc[df['Country'].isin(top_countries)].copy()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 27,
   "id": "5a07fd2e-0372-4515-97fa-6573326b2dcd",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Calculating total medal counts in each sport for the top countires\n",
    "\n",
    "country_sport = (\n",
    "    top_df.groupby(['Country', 'Sport'])\n",
    "        .size()\n",
    "        .reset_index(name='Medal_Count')\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 28,
   "id": "1bd306b8-072a-46b4-a185-5ed7e1b9e087",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Calculating the 3 top sports for each country\n",
    "\n",
    "top_sports_per_country = (\n",
    "    country_sport.sort_values(['Country', 'Medal_Count'], ascending=[True, False])\n",
    "        .groupby('Country')\n",
    "        .head(3)  \n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 29,
   "id": "c4ac3eda-84d4-4ef8-9712-4553c36fa4ef",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
